dct_description_sm: This tabular data, prepared by Data You Can Use, presents the median sales price of residential properties by census tract in the city of Milwaukee, Wisconsin from 2019-2023. The data is sourced from the City of Milwaukee Assessor's Office, Milwaukee Open Data Portal, and utilizes 2020 Census tracts. For more information, please visit Data You Can Use.
